name: Ring Dragon
description:
16.1" x 10.7". Printed on High quality 310g.s.m Hahnemuhle Etching paper.  This heavyweight etching
board is silky smooth with a fine
surface texture. It is one of the most
popular media worldwide for artwork
& photography. This paper provides longevity to the life of the print, and is extremely durable against fading.

The print is Signed by me, the artist. It also comes with a small border for ease of framing. (Frame not included)
